45:40.806 --> 45:41.873
Your...

45:41.907 --> 45:44.976
VARGAS: Did I tell you
what I like about this place,

45:45.010 --> 45:46.344
Minnesota?

45:47.345 --> 45:53.018
It's so perfectly,
sublimely bland.

45:55.653 --> 45:59.490
Have you been to the Danube?
Or Gansu?

46:00.425 --> 46:02.427
And the African continent...
Forget it.

46:02.460 --> 46:04.495
North and south. Anarchy.

46:04.963 --> 46:08.399
And, yes, you can still find
some relative stability

46:08.433 --> 46:12.804
in the brutal nation states,
North Korea...

46:13.104 --> 46:15.306
Putin's done some great things
with Russia.

46:15.340 --> 46:17.442
You just have to know
which palms to grease.

46:17.475 --> 46:19.811
But one wearies
of the constant

46:19.845 --> 46:22.948
remunerations and
the petty shakedowns...

46:23.648 --> 46:26.484
Meet the new boss,
same as the old boss.

46:26.784 --> 46:28.219
Am I right?

46:28.719 --> 46:30.021
Mr. Vargas?

46:30.055 --> 46:31.356
Please, Sy...

46:32.190 --> 46:34.525
Call me V.M.

46:34.960 --> 46:35.961
Eh?

46:36.527 --> 46:37.762
We're partners now.

46:37.795 --> 46:39.330
We are not partners.

46:39.364 --> 46:40.832
