with interest.

46:46.137 --> 46:48.373
(SPEAKING FRENCH)

46:52.477 --> 46:54.545
You see, that's the problem
with you Americans.

46:54.579 --> 46:56.214
You watch too many movies,
and you think

46:56.247 --> 46:58.683
the deal can always
be changed, and it can't.

46:58.716 --> 47:01.186
We're partners now,
and that's all there is to it.

47:01.219 --> 47:02.820
So, you might as
well just lie back,

47:02.854 --> 47:05.823
as they say,
and enjoy yourselves.

47:13.098 --> 47:15.533
Let me tell you what it is
that attracts me

47:15.566 --> 47:17.903
to the parking lot business,
yours in particular.

47:17.936 --> 47:19.270
It's three things.

47:20.071 --> 47:21.606
It runs on cash.

47:22.607 --> 47:24.709
You don't use technology.

47:24.742 --> 47:28.379
