and for how long?

47:33.885 --> 47:37.889
Mr. Vargas, V.M., if I may...

47:38.289 --> 47:40.391
We show, in our books...

47:40.425 --> 47:43.761
We show a very consistent,
very steady,

47:43.794 --> 47:45.563
predictable income

47:45.596 --> 47:47.232
from lot to lot,

47:47.265 --> 47:50.068
consistent with
several urban volume factors.

47:51.236 --> 47:53.905
