goosing those numbers...

47:53.939 --> 47:58.776
Well, (SCOFFS)
so we buy more lots.

47:59.644 --> 48:02.547
Maybe branch out,
start developing

48:02.580 --> 48:06.351
some multi-function commercial
and residential properties,

48:06.384 --> 48:08.253
a new stadium, perhaps.

48:12.290 --> 48:13.458
